Step 1: Install MiddleWare Server ie Application Server
Step 2: Configure System DSN for Middleware Server

Driver Class for Type3 Drivers: ids.sql.IDSDriver
jdbc URL: jdbc:/ids://localhost:12/con?dsn=sysdsntype3 -->sysdsntyp3 need to configure in middleware Server in
                         |       |                          For DB Connect
                         |       |
                         |    Default port for IDS
                         |
                    Server URL
                    
                    
